item.title: CVE-2023-5340|2023-11-20T18:55:01.256Z -- unknown -- five%20star%20restaurant%20menu%20and%20food%20ordering
item.description: The Five Star Restaurant Menu and Food Ordering WordPress plugin before 2.4.11 unserializes user input via an AJAX action available to unauthenticated users, allowing them to perform PHP Object Injection when a suitable gadget is present on the blog.
